The 2019 Cape Town Marathon will be taking place on Sunday, 15 September. The list of road closures for the race are below: CAPE TOWN - The 2019 Cape Town Marathon will be taking place on Sunday, 15 September. The list of road closures for the race are below: SATURDAY, 14 SEPTEMBER 2019 GREEN POINT  SUNDAY, 15 SEPTEMBER 2019 SEA POINT, GREEN POINT & DE WATERKANT  CITY / CBD  SOUTHERN SUBURBS (WOODSTOCK, SALT RIVER, OBSERVATORY, MOWBRAY, ROSEBANK, RONDEBOSCH, NEWLANDS AND CLAREMONT) 